title: Display property 'none' not taking effect in new PDF emitter
description: When the display property of an item is set to 'none' in the new PDF emitter, the item should disappear. However, in the current implementation, the item is still visible.
OB: The label is still visible in the PDF preview.
EB: The label should disappear in the PDF preview.
SR:
To reproduce this issue: 
1. Open the PDF emitter tool. 
2. Set the display property of an item to 'none'. 
3. Preview the PDF. 
4. Observe that the label is still visible in the PDF preview.
